bilingual.source: He ran quickly to catch the bus.
bilingual.target: 他迅速地跑去赶公交车。

bilingual.source: The doctor quickly bound up his arm.
bilingual.target: 医生迅速地包扎了他的手臂。

bilingual.source: The doctor quickly binds up a wound.

The waitress quickly brought us our food.
bilingual.target: 女服务员迅速地为我们上了菜。
工人们迅速地卸下了货物。

list.abstract: quickly，音标 [ˈkwɪkli]，英语单词。作副词为迅速地、立刻、立即。例句：He replied to my letter very quickly .（他很快给我回了信。） quickly的近义词有rapidly、fast、promptly等。反义词有slowly。

yingyinNormal.en: In with garlic and the ginger and as you drop it in, very quickly give that a good stir.
yingyinNormal.zh: 把大蒜和生姜扔进去，非常迅速地好好炒一下。

yingyinNormal.en: Then have faith you made the right choice, sir. Whatever faith I have is quickly evaporating.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那就相信你做出了正确的决定，先生。我的信念正在迅速地消失殆尽。

yingyinNormal.en: Now the wok is still hot, so very quickly I'm going to add in the shitake mushrooms. And then give that a good stir.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在锅还是热的，我要迅速地倒入香菇片，然后翻炒均匀。

yingyinNormal.en: Thanks for coming so quickly, Mark.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢你来的这么快，马克。

yingyinNormal.en: I came as quickly as I could. Okay. Why?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我尽最快速度赶来了。好的，为什么？

yingyinNormal.en: You'd be just as amazed how quickly it goes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想像不到时间过得有多快。

yingyinNormal.en: These giant wind farms are quickly coming online.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些硕大的风电场即将迅速投用。

yingyinNormal.en: Quickly. We must fix the Slushious and find Mimom.
yingyinNormal.zh: 快点，我们得快点修好飞船找到迈玛。

yingyinNormal.en: Johnny, have you tried this Slurpee? Not that quickly, hon.
yingyinNormal.zh: 约翰，你有尝过这思乐冰吗？不要喝这么快，亲爱的。

yingyinNormal.en: George. Don't drink your juice too quickly. George drank his juice too quickly, and now he has hiccups.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治，果汁不要喝得那么快。乔治果汁喝得太快，结果现在开始打嗝了。

yingyinNormal.en: George. If you drink too quickly, you will get hiccups again. I'm not as little as George. I can drink juice as quickly as I want to.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治，你喝得那么快，等一会又要打嗝了。不过我可比乔治大多了，所以我可以想喝多快就喝多快。

yingyinNormal.en: Quickly now, children. The show is about to begin. Madame Gazelle, I need a toilet. Oh, Pedro. Sorry. Sorry. Thank you. Quickly now, Pedro.
yingyinNormal.zh: 快点孩子们，演出马上就要开始了！额，抱歉羚羊夫人，我想上厕所。哦，佩德罗！抱歉，额，抱歉！谢谢！快去快回，佩德罗！

yingyinNormal.en: You can post the card here. Goodbye, postcard. Fly home quickly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你可以把明信片投在这。再见明信片，快点飞回家。

yingyinNormal.en: You can post the card here. Goodbye, postcard. Fly home quickly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你可以把明信片投在这。再见明信片，快点飞回家。

yingyinNormal.en: And this is about an inheritance? Yes, it is. You catch on quickly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 诉讼是关于遗产吗？是的，你反应还挺快。

yingyinNormal.en: Of course, it quickly became clear that it wasn't just about that day.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然，很快我就明白了，不仅仅是因为那天。

yingyinNormal.en: The train is going slowly uphill. the train is going quickly downhill.
yingyinNormal.zh: 火车慢慢地爬上了山。然后火车快速地下山了。

yingyinNormal.en: The train is going slowly uphills. the train is going quickly downhills.
yingyinNormal.zh: 火车正在缓慢的上坡。火车正在快速下坡。

yingyinNormal.en: While that's cooking, I'm going to very quickly chop up some vegetables.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在煮面过程中，我会快速地切碎一些蔬菜。

yingyinNormal.en: Right. To the hospital. Quickly, now. Do not panic. Bye. Bye. Good luck.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在！赶紧去医院，立刻就去，千万别惊慌！再见！再见！祝好运。
